videos.description: Tyus Battle fakes out his defender and drains a long jumper for Syracuse.
videos.headline: Battle shakes defender to make 3-pointer

videos.description: Frank Howard and Tyus Battle each sink 3-pointers to extend the Orange's lead and force Wake Forest to call a timeout.
videos.headline: Syracuse creates momentum with back-to-back 3-pointers

videos.description: Oshae Brissett gets the inbounds pass and finishes with a two-handed flush for Syracuse.
videos.headline: Brissett throws it down vs. Wake Forest

videos.description: Frank Howard finds Paschal Chukwu under the rim for a Syracuse dunk.
videos.headline: Howard connects with Chukwu for alley-oop

videos.description: Keyshawn Woods gets a perfect pass to Doral Moore who throws down a sweet slam for Wake Forest.
videos.headline: Wake Forest answers with Moore dunk

videos.description: Tyus Battle forces a turnover and quickly slams it down on the other end, pumping up the home crowd.
videos.headline: Battle steals and slams for Syracuse

videos.description: Bryant Crawford drains a corner 3-pointer to cut Syracuse's lead with a minute to play.
videos.headline: Crawford shrinks lead with 3-pointer
